<view class="brand-container"><view class="header-section"><view class="header-bg"><image src="/static/img/1.png" mode="aspectFill"></image></view><view class="header-content"><view class="logo-wrapper"><image class="logo" src="/static/img/brand.png"></image></view><view class="brand-name">潮汐健身中心</view><view class="brand-slogan">Tidal Fitness · 开启健康生活</view></view></view><view class="content-section"><view class="intro-card"><view class="card-header"><view class="card-title">关于我们</view><view class="card-line"></view></view><view class="intro-content"><view class="intro-text"> 潮汐健身中心是一家专注于提供高品质健身服务的现代化健身场所。我们拥有先进的健身设备、专业的教练团队和舒适的运动环境，致力于为每一位会员打造专属的健康生活方式。 </view><view class="intro-text"> 我们提供多样化的健身课程，包括瑜伽、普拉提、动感单车、搏击操、力量训练等，满足不同会员的健身需求。无论你是健身新手还是资深爱好者，都能在这里找到适合自己的训练方式。 </view><view class="intro-features"><view class="feature-item"><view class="feature-icon"><image src="/static/img/practice.png"></image></view><view class="feature-text">专业教练</view></view><view class="feature-item"><view class="feature-icon"><image src="/static/img/card.png"></image></view><view class="feature-text">多样课程</view></view><view class="feature-item"><view class="feature-icon"><image src="/static/img/activity.png"></image></view><view class="feature-text">优质环境</view></view><view class="feature-item"><view class="feature-icon"><image src="/static/img/service.png"></image></view><view class="feature-text">贴心服务</view></view></view></view></view><view class="contact-card"><view class="card-header"><view class="card-title">联系我们</view><view class="card-line"></view></view><view class="contact-list"><view class="contact-item"><view class="contact-left"><view class="contact-icon"><image src="/static/img/map.png"></image></view><view class="contact-label">地址</view></view><view class="contact-value">{{bussinessInfo.address}}</view></view><view class="contact-item"><view class="contact-left"><view class="contact-icon"><image src="/static/img/telephone.png"></image></view><view class="contact-label">电话</view></view><view class="contact-value">{{bussinessInfo.phone}}</view></view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['open',['$event']]]]]}}" class="contact-item" bindtap="__e"><view class="contact-left"><view class="contact-icon"><image src="/static/img/wx.png"></image></view><view class="contact-label">微信</view></view><view class="contact-value">{{bussinessInfo.wx}}</view><view class="contact-arrow">›</view></view></view></view></view><uni-popup class="vue-ref" vue-id="85dd0ffc-1" type="center" data-ref="wx" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><view class="wx-popup"><view class="popup-header"><text class="popup-title">潮汐健身中心</text><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['e0',['$event']]]]]}}" class="popup-close" bindtap="__e">×</text></view><view class="popup-content"><image class="qrcode" src="/static/img/wxerweima.jpg"></image><text class="popup-tip">微信扫码联系客服</text></view></view></uni-popup></view>